com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.graphql

Class GraphQlVariableDeclaration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.graphql.GraphQlVariableDeclaration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphQL

    public abstract class GraphQlVariableDeclaration
extends java.lang.Object
implements GraphQL
    A GraphQL variable declaration. Can only be of default scalar types and their corresponding arrays. Variable declarations should be created using one of the many 'of' factory methods
    Since:
    1.28.0
    Author:
    S.Roughley knime@vernalis.com
